          INT.   CARDUCCI'S ANTIQUES   NIGHT
          
          The store itself looks like an antique - old wood panelling and
          shelving, Victorian display cases, and faded wallpaper.  It is
          grimy, dusty, and dimly-lit - and apparently unattended.
          
